sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Domain as DichVuNguon
actor User as NguoiDung
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant NotiSvc as NotificationService
participant NotiDb as Mongo_Notification

Note over Domain,NotiDb: Chặng 2 - Lỗi token nội bộ và thao tác đọc
Domain->>Gateway: POST /api/notifications
Gateway->>NotiSvc: Validate internal token
alt Token sai hoặc thiếu
  NotiSvc-->>Domain: 401/403
else Token đúng
  NotiSvc->>NotiDb: Lưu thông báo
end

User->>Gateway: PATCH /api/notifications/read-all
Gateway->>NotiSvc: Mark read
NotiSvc->>NotiDb: Update isRead/readAt
NotiSvc-->>User: 200
